WEBVTT

00:04:56.819 --> 00:05:01.382
came together to create
the next big manufacturing reinvention.

00:05:01.406 --> 00:05:02.664
Bingo!

00:05:02.688 --> 00:05:05.171
This is the fourth
manufacturing revolution,

00:05:05.195 --> 00:05:06.859
and it's happening right now.

00:05:07.355 --> 00:05:10.621
Major technologies are entering
the manufacturing space,

00:05:10.645 --> 00:05:11.795
big time.

00:05:12.316 --> 00:05:15.412
They will boost industrial productivity
by more than a third.

00:05:16.217 --> 00:05:19.943
This is massive, and it will do
a lot in creating growth.

00:05:21.286 --> 00:05:23.092
Let me tell you about some of them.

00:05:24.091 --> 00:05:26.990
Have you already met advanced
manufacturing robots?

00:05:27.583 --> 00:05:29.678
They are the size of humans,

00:05:29.702 --> 00:05:31.723
they actually collaborate with them,